  shortDescription: The house phone. It hasn't rung in a while.
  fullStory: David calls when he can. The conversations get harder.
  marthaContext: "Martha answers the phone when Robert can't. She and David don't
    talk about the hard things \u2014 they just coordinate care and pretend everything
    is fine."
  davidContext: "David calls because he doesn't know what else to do. Hearing Robert's
    voice \u2014 even diminished \u2014 is better than imagining the worst."
